devalue by more than your down payment.

00:13:09.742 --> 00:13:12.575
But, even more than that,
there's an interest rate risk.

00:13:12.575 --> 00:13:14.777
Because what happens if
the bank lends you money,

00:13:14.777 --> 00:13:17.084
lends you a big chunk of money at 5%,

00:13:17.084 --> 00:13:20.123
